		<articleText><![CDATA[<p class="leading13">This is a content popup that you can use to display extended details about your portfolio item. You can add and position unlimited images, as3 swfs, html text blocks, or even a slideshow anywhere throughout the page. You can set this page's width, height, opacity from XML.  You can choose to use a manual scrollbar which you can skin from XML, or choose to use the hover scroll feature, which automatically scrolls the page when the user hovers over the content area.  You can also set the top and bottom margin from XML and position your page to be either left aligned, right aligned, center aligned,or a static X,Y position.  The goal was to give you total creative liberty when skinning this template to fit your project, without having to be code freaks like us and constantly open flash to make changes. Also if you do not need a full page to display your extended portfolio you can choose to use any one of the ten image popups outlined on layout 2 under the content tab!</p>]]></articleText>
